body_html: I have a similar issue, I think. If I quantize an inception v3 graph on Ubuntu (Intel x86_64) and test on the same platform then I get reasonable results. If I try to use the quantized graph on Linux (ARMv7) then the results are quite bad. Is there something specific to a platform that is done in quantization process? I apologize I have not investigated the quantization code/build settings in greater detail.
